Made by Kill3rTomato (AKA killertomatoe, wurmy1029)
Made for 4HM Gun Game
Supports 40 players total (20 Ts, 20 CTs)
Has 2 BuyZones (1 T, 1 CT) at spawn.
Give credit where credit is due.
Contact - wurmy1029@yahoo.com

Hope you like this map. It's made mostly for gun game
but does work for normal play. Also notice, it is meant for online play. Playing with bots won't work well because for some odd
reason they like to jump off and die. I don't know why, they
just do that. Either way have fun :)

NOTE: I haven't tested it with real people. When you do (If you do) please e-mail me (wurmy1029@yahoo.com) and send comments of the map. Thanks!

- Kill3rTomato
